00:00:00.001 --> 00:00:00.005
Key Considerations for Using Gloves.

00:00:00.540 --> 00:00:03.845
Three sizes gloves on Box are highlight in Small, Medium and Large.

00:00:41.841 --> 00:00:58.000
1. Choose as being the best or most suitable glove size that fits your hands well.
2. While your gloves are on, do not touch your face or common surfaces.
3. When your experiment is complete, remove the gloves and wash your hands before exiting the lab.